OL,3,CDebt and despair - the Oldham
OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,FFive years on, repairs are still
OL,8,Fongoing and they have yet to return.
OL,9,FBut management company RMG continue to
OL,10,Fcharge resident for management fees.
OL,12,FFozia Malik is at the end of her
OL,13,Ftether, forced to live in student
OL,14,Fhalls while she waits to move back in.
OL,16,FShe said: "They just send us invoices
OL,17,Fevery year - four to five thousand
OL,18,Fpounds, and they say 'we are doing
OL,19,Fthis, we are doing that' and add more
OL,20,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
