OL,3,CDebt and despair - the Oldham
OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,F"I've paid more than #25,000 I think.
OL,8,FWhen every year goes by that we don't
OL,9,Fget answers from RMG, we ask for a
OL,10,Ftime frame but don't get one."
OL,12,FLee Ashworth and his daughter Sarah
OL,13,Fown and rented out two of the flats at
OL,14,FVictory, and together they have lost
OL,15,Fthousands to RMG and paid thousands
OL,16,Fmore in rent.
OL,18,FLee has been diagnosed with leukemia,
OL,19,Fwhile his wife has a serious brain
OL,20,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
