OL,7,FLee said: "We can't do anything about
OL,8,Fit. We couldn't afford legal
OL,9,Frepresentation. This is a very big
OL,10,Fcompany and we can't do anything in
OL,11,Fthat respect."
OL,13,FCladding safety campaigners the
OL,14,FManchester Cladiators have got behind
OL,15,FFozia's calls to stop billing tenants
OL,16,Fand leaseholders for a building they
OL,17,Fcannot live in.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
