OL,3,CDebt and despair - the Oldham
OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,FIn a statement they told us: "We
OL,8,Funderstand the ongoing concerns of
OL,9,Fresidents and want to reassure
OL,10,Feveryone that their safety remains our
OL,11,Fhighest priority.
OL,13,FThis is a complex situation, and we
OL,14,Fare fully committed to resolving it as
OL,15,Fswiftly and thoroughly as possible so
OL,16,Fpeople can live in these homes again.
OL,18,FWe can confirm that works are
OL,19,Fprogressing. We will continue to
OL,20,Fprovide regular updates as progress is
OL,21,Fmade."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
