OL,4,Cresidents locked out of their fire-
OL,5,Chazard flats
OL,7,FIn a further statement, RMG added: "A
OL,8,Fresident meeting is due to take place
OL,9,Fon 26 June to provide updates.
OL,10,FRemedial works are progressing as
OL,11,Fplanned, and we remain on track for
OL,12,Fthe previously communicated target of
OL,13,Fmid-July for completion, which will
OL,14,Fthen be subject to final confirmation
OL,15,Ffrom Greater Manchester Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Service for the prohibition to
OL,17,Fbe lifted."
